metadata.name: Unearthing Love in Mexico's Los Muertos
metadata.description:
Love is a powerful emotion that transcends time ano space. A love story that transcends all boundaries - even death. Their connection was strong and the vibrant colors and lively music of their lives was a testament to that love.

The characters depicted in this series are entirely fictitious.
